snippet.textDisplay: I've watched this video about 100 times...I had to read the English subtitles...I'm not Indian...I'm Italian...but the message in this song is very deep...I feel for the Punjabi community...because it must hurt to feel the loss in culture and traditions ..I First listened to this song because I love the Punjabi culture and the people are very nice and welcoming....i find the music is very interesting and uplifting with great instruments and musicianship...I wish the Punjabi communities worldwide the best to hang on to the beautiful traditions and culture to keep going.Peace and Love
